            </div>
            <section class="mb-4">
                <p>
                    We are here for you, to provide you with self-drive cars and bikes. You can rent a car or bike for long travels,
                    hill drives, chilling around with loved ones, business needs and lot more.
                    Simply said we have ride for all of us.
                    We as a team are working towards the most luxurious and ecological ways for all of us to travel.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
                        <h5 class="text-uppercase">Company</h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0" id="list">
                            <li>
                                <input type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary text-white" id="about" value="about" />
